  qdrant-timeout-ms: 10000
  file-globs: all indexable files

  TUI shortcuts:
  /index auto-warm on|off
  /index require-embeddings on|off
  /index embedding-model <name|default>
  /index edit
  Use [query_project_index] in config.toml for backend, qdrant, file_globs, and non-TUI edits.
